title: #92Noon! Micheletti/Tollackson/Levine/LaVelle/Kurtz/Reid/
description: Pat Micheletti kicks off the show talking Wild hockey, Spencer Tollackson calls in to talk Gopher Hoops, Twins GM Thad Levine joins the show to talk spring training, more Twins talk with the Star Tribune from LaVelle E. Neal III, and Bob Kurtz and Tom Reid join #92Noon live from Barclays Center in Brooklyn to preview the Wild-Islanders game!
